leios.theme.plasmoids.digitalclock (1.0.2) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Fix postrm removing packaged files: do not call kpackagetool6 -r,
    which deletes files owned by dpkg under /usr/share/plasma/plasmoids/.
  * Refresh the Plasma shell and clear QML caches on install, upgrade
    and removal so UI changes are visible immediately via apt.
  * Switch debian/rules install step from rsync to cp -a and remove
    rsync from runtime Depends.

 -- Linus Fischer <leicraft@leicraftmc.de>  Tue, 14 Jul 2026 12:00:00 +0200

leios.theme.plasmoids.digitalclock (1.0.1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Add postinst/postrm maintainer scripts to register, upgrade and
    unregister the global plasmoid via kpackagetool6 -g.
  * Refresh the Plasma shell and clear QML caches on install, upgrade
    and removal so UI changes are visible immediately via apt.
  * Switch debian/rules install step from rsync to cp -a and remove
    rsync from runtime Depends.

 -- Linus Fischer <leicraft@leicraftmc.de>  Tue, 14 Jul 2026 12:00:00 +0200

leios.theme.plasmoids.digitalclock (1.0.0) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Initial release.
  * Fork of KDE Plasma Digital Clock plasmoid for LeiOS.
  * Fix spacing bug in automatic date display mode.

 -- Linus Fischer <leicraft@leicraftmc.de>  Mon, 13 Jul 2026 12:00:00 +0200
